    // 1. All '0's followed by at most one '1': "00...01" or "00...0". (Structure $0^*1?$)
    // 2. At most one '1' followed by all '0's: "100...0" or "00...0". (Structure $1?0^*$)
    // 3. All '1's: "11...1".
    // 4. All '0's: "00...0".
    //
