    // 011: Requires $s_i=0, s_j=1, s_k=1$ with $i<j<k$.
    // 110: Requires $s_i=1, s_j=1, s_k=0$ with $i<j<k$.
    //
    // If a string is $0^*1^*$, it contains "011" iff there is at least one '0' and at least two '1's.
    // If a string is $1^*0^*$, it contains "110" iff there are at least two '1's and at least one '0'.
    //
    // A string $s$ is connected if and only if:
    // (It is not $0^*1^*$ with $|0| \ge 1, |1| \ge 2$) AND (It is not $1^*0^*$ with $|1| \ge 2, |0| \ge 1$).
